Description_lang: Launches a void missile at a nearby location, inflicting $s1 Shadow damage and applying $@spellname306279 to all enemies in a $A1 yard radius. If this damage is not soaked it will trigger $@spellname306637,  inflicting $306637s1 Shadow damage, applying $@spellname306279 and Silence all players for $306637d. Another missile will then be launched at another nearby location. This can occur up 5 times.
